name: Clipboard::Type
detail:
This type is an `enum class` with following values:
* `Clipboard::Type::CopyPaste`
* `Clipboard::Type::Drag`
* `Clipboard::Type::Find`
* `Clipboard::Type::Font`
* `Clipboard::Type::Selection`

The `Drag`, `Find`, `Font` clipboards are only available on macOS, and the
`Selection` clipboard is only available on Linux.
